{
  "texts": [
    "Their per-formance is also susceptible to environmental conditions such as humidity and temperature, which can introduce noise and lower accuracy.",
    "Moreover, these systems often struggle to replicate the full sensitivity and nuance of human perception, particularly in capturing subtle aroma interactions or texture-related cues.",
    "The lack of standardized datasets and benchmarking protocols further limits reproducibility and cross-platform validation.",
    "Addressing these challenges is essential for improving the robustness, interpretability, and generalizability of AI-assisted sensory systems.",
    "To quantitatively support the historical development of AI in olfaction and gustation, we conducted a bibliometric analysis using Google Scholar."
  ]
}